            Novo nome:
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name">
            <br />

            Novo e-mail:
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="email" name="email">
            <br />

            Nova data de Nascimento (formato DD/MM/AAAA):
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="birth_date" name="birth_date" onkeypress="return isInteger(event.which, event.keyCode)">
